{"type": "article", "id": 21902, "title": "做了几十年时尚编辑和造型师，她的衣橱里都有什么？", "description": "琳琅满目、色彩斑斓的鞋履、包包可能是很多人心中的理想衣橱", "date": "2016-02-04T12:19:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7240, "name": "造型师"}, {"id": 23146, "name": "杂志封面"}, {"id": 17030, "name": "奢侈品牌"}, {"id": 993, "name": "高跟鞋"}, {"id": 1492, "name": "钱包"}, {"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}, {"id": 1819, "name": "ELLE"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 136, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151403b8hEAxgTI4RWX2fV.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这里要介绍的 Lori Goldstein，没听说过这个名字也没关系，随便说几条她的履历就够了。比如作为入行 38 年的顶级造型师，是众多最具影响力的封面和广告背后的人物，为<i> Vogue、W、Vanity Fair、ELLE</i> 等杂志封面的拍摄做造型；担任过麦当娜、碧昂斯、Terry Richardson、Annie Leibovitz 等人的御用造型师；还有 为 Prada 、Versace、 Hermès、Tiffany &amp; Co 等众多奢侈品牌的广告大片作创意指导……</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021513463RPuZ7pAlcmwbIi2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151347A6g0nXK51TFrYtIH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151348ndMyhspcqHJ82eGl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">同时还身兼设计师、作家、编辑等身份，2012  年起受邀担任美国<i> ELLE</i> 特约编辑。2013 年 Lori 推出了自己的首本个人时装书 <i>Style is Instinct </i>后，在众多时尚类必读书籍榜单的前列都有这本书的身影。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151348BDVsh0y9CtnOmTUG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75114504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">这样一位时尚“老咖”，对于如何穿衣、如何展开时尚事业一定会有很多话想说（所以她出书了），并且总是指导别人穿搭，那么她自己的衣橱呢？</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.thecoveteur.com/lori-goldstein/?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=socialmedia&amp;utm_campaign=facebook-throwbackthursday\">The Coveteur 就探访了她在纽约的家</a>，再这样一个色彩斑斓、极具魅力的空间里，你会看到她各式各样的单品。她自己也承认有点收藏癖——“过去这些年我购买又出售、交易过很多东西，就是为了得到完美又出人意料的收藏。”</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151349YfISwe8uMPBqsQEz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0px;\"><i>Hermès 包</i><br></figure><div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"><i></i></figure><p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151350QavuiT1pgjZmtNM3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"><i></i></figure><p></p>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"><br></figure><p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151351pwXPRaeikDGAfZ0c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></figure><p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0px;\"><i>高跟鞋 Pierre Hardy  </i><br></figure><p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151352Pt5Hw8XDWiNmTvel.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.275\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></figure><p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><i>高跟鞋  Nicholas Kirkwood</i><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">“诚实地说，我就压根不记得什么时候不沉迷于服装，我有一件带圆点的比基尼，我喜欢它的款式和颜色，那是我 4 岁时候得到的礼物。”</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\" class=\"\">高中时她就被同学们评选为“最想模仿穿着的对象”。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p><i></i></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151353CE0aVegDjBQYizPO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">平底鞋 Céline／夹克  Gary Graham／高跟鞋 Pierre Hardy</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021513555k7EFBlNs6aJuihP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8212963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Chanel 鞋</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151356vZDCEFkcabqod4YU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Céline 与 Prada 鞋</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151357k6WE9gI1T3KNXufd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.90185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">各品牌的太阳镜</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151358nDZvPYXIc1U4sorE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.90740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Prada 和 LV 的零钱包</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021513592rLaEosgWVUC3d1j.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151359JzEb31cqxdTSAFMY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>彩色上衣  Proenza Schouler</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151400IvQbrtkfpg8CRhFG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>上衣 Marni、鞋子 Nicholas Kirkwood／鞋 Chloé、大衣 Marni</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021514014Ib9xLinWZPBhkwN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021514011R4BAr2T9lLFjs6z.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>包 Hermès、鞋 Dries Van Noten</p></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p>Lori 说自己的风格很 70 年代，从摇滚到罗密欧与朱丽叶，总是混搭、层叠以及使用很多配件。她的衣柜就是自我的延伸，充满活力又独特。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151402r3vndFwLYTplM1HP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50082645\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自：The Coveteur </p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}